Start the redirect server

Usage:
  redirectly [CONFIG --port PORT]
  redirectly --init
  redirectly --help | --version

Options:
  -p --port PORT
    Listening port [default: 3000]

  -i --init
    Create a sample config file and exit

  -h --help
    Show this help

  --version
    Show version number

Parameters:
  CONFIG
    Path to config file [default: redirects.ini]

Examples:
  redirectly --init
  redirectly config.ini
